      <div style="font-size: 10px; color: #8A8A86; line-height: 1.6; align-self: stretch; max-width: 1240px; width: 100%; margin: 0 auto">Ten random products styled with the current template, format and settings. Apply a preset or switch template/format in the sidebar and the whole batch restyles instantly; Shuffle deals ten new products. Export renders each at full production size. Export all MP4 uses your Animation tab setup (effects, easing, layer toggles, image cycle) and records each video in real time, one after another — keep the tab visible and allow multiple downloads.</div>
      <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 18px; align-self: stretch; max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%">
